msgid " You can select multiple categories of the correct type."
msgstr "Du kan vælge flere kategorier af den korrekte type."

#: templates/campaign/campaign-form.html:112
msgid "Depth must be set to 0 for all categories in a Wiki Loves campaign."
msgstr "Dybden skal sættes til 0 for alle kategorier i en Wiki Loves-kampagne."

#: templates/campaign/campaign-form.html:114
msgid "Requires categories of the form images from Wiki Loves <strong><em>project</em></strong> in a specific <strong><em>year</em></strong>, eg “Images from Wiki Loves <strong><em>Africa</em></strong> <strong><em>2019</em></strong>” (change <strong><em>project</em></strong> and year as <strong><em>required</em></strong>)"
